r.com/blog/update-wordpress/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:4;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:58:\"9 Websites With Animations That Inspire Us as Web Creators\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:215:\"Websites with animations are a key ingredient for visual storytelling. Check out these nine examples of websites whove added advanced design effects to their sites and have truly mastered the art of animation.\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1592314235\";s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:128:\"https://elementor.com/blog/examples-websites-animations/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}}', 'no'),
